snippet.title: 🎮 TankWars.io New Tank Classes & Tank Ability
snippet.description:
New TankWars .io Update - Tank Classes and a Ability
► Play TankWars.io: http://tankwars.io/
Presenting STOMP, Mammoth tank & Scout tank!

See amazing community skins!
Make your own awesome TankWars .io skin!
All in the 🎮 TankWars.io unique customization editor!

▼ TankWars.io Videos
🎨 New Maps Sketches https://youtu.be/0T3ax3XWn0g
⚡ Scout Tank gameplay https://youtu.be/j-ZG9TVkko0
💪 Mammoth Tank gameplay https://youtu.be/4u9AbxcAW9Y
✔️ TankWars.io tanks gameplay https://youtu.be/dOw47w3CmGQ
🎮 Tank Teleport Power-up https://youtu.be/hNIoxU83SaI
